An experimental MLIR backend for the Exo programming language.

## Dependencies

```bash
# macOS
brew install llvm pkg-config google-benchmark clang lld ninja ccache
# might need to update path
export PATH="$(brew --prefix llvm)/bin:$PATH"

# setup
uv venv
uv sync --all-extras
source .venv/bin/activate
```

## Usage

Run the compiler:

```bash
exo-mlir <source.py> [--target {exo,builtin,scf,lowered,llvm}] [-o output.mlir]
# e.g. exo-mlir benchmarks/level1/axpy.py --target llvm -o out/axpy.mlir
```

## Benchmarks

```bash
snakemake
```

## Tests

```bash
pytest tests/
lit tests/filecheck/
```
